            <h1>Our Mission</h1>
            <p>WordPress is software designed for everyone with emphasis on accessibility, performance, security, and usability. We believe great software should work with little setup so you can focus on sharing  your story, product, or services freely. The basic WordPress software is simple and predictable to easily get started, yet also offers a solid array of features for growth and success.</p>
        <p>We believe in democratizing publishing and the freedoms that come with open source. Gathered behind this idea is a large community of people dedicated to this project. The WordPress community is growing and inclusive. Their passion is what drives the success of WordPress and, in turn, helps you reach your goals.</p>
            
